Description: Downloads, processes, and formats climate data from the
    Climatic Research Unit (CRU) Time-Series (TS) v4.09 dataset
    (Harris et al., 2020). Provides functions to retrieve monthly
    precipitation, minimum temperature, maximum temperature, and
    mean temperature data at 0.5 degree resolution for the period
    1901-2024. Includes tools to convert CRU data to 'terra'
    SpatRaster objects and to calculate the 19 bioclimatic variables
    commonly used in species distribution modeling.
